Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.87,0:01:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.34,0:01:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把惑星聯合宇宙軍的威信\N和技術的精粹集中起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.38,0:01:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是最新銳的巡洋艦\N阿蘇號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.55,0:01:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面\N把有不良記錄的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.16,0:01:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收容起來的舊式驅逐艦\N微風號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有什麼好裝備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是它有其他艦沒有的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.67,0:02:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被解體的話\N總覺得有些感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.61,0:02:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.04,0:02:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你雖然答得這樣乾脆\N可是你人還是來這裡了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.38,0:02:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走累了…\N陸地就不再有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩累了…\N也並不是年老的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.05,0:02:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有問題\N可是他曾經是我們的艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.59,0:02:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和大家一樣\N只是我是艦長而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.06,0:02:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不遲\N阿蘇號在等著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘇號也需要自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.07,0:02:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由里子小姐自由對妳而言\N很重要吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了誰的自由和責任?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.57,0:02:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切斷啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.97,0:02:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切斷了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.41,0:02:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,完全斷決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.68,0:02:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不管怎麼斷決\N我也不後悔、不反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣\N你不想搭乘阿蘇號嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…那艘…\N是軍艦吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.62,0:02:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長你,已經變了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.56,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人吃驚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.96,0:03:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.26,0:03:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和艦長兩個人一起這樣喝酒\N是第一次…不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心藏砰砰跳\N並不是因為酒的關係喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.10,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再回到\N遇到艦長之前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.31,0:03:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,有沒有把我的事情\N告訴山本君他們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.05,0:03:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,現在大家可能正在\N拼命找艦長吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.16,0:04:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找我也沒什麼用呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,大家把艦長的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由里子小姐\N妳不是已經決定做地上勤務了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由里子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.81,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該照由里子小姐心裡所想的\N去做…這樣是最好的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.08,0:04:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山本君他們也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.45,0:04:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只此一次的人生\N不要被人家弄的暈頭轉向的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.19,0:04:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己喜歡的事\N照自己的意思去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.82,0:04:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照自己的意思…去做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照自己的意思去做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.53,0:04:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由里子小姐碰見山本君他們時\N請這樣告訴他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.87,0:04:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.88,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子好幾次、好幾次\N真的好幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.29,0:05:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都被騙啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長,我…要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?現在馬上?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.76,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,回去告訴大家艦長的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己喜歡的事情\N照自己的意思去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,大家已經…\N差不多都知道了,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為不知道才會去找艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由里子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有酒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.87,0:05:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝,可能無法再次和艦長…\N不,或許再也見不到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,你的溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由里子小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.88,0:06:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.23,0:06:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 妳說什麼?\N- 艦長是不回來囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家難得替他這麼擔心!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.31,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧!不把他好好修理一頓\N我的氣不會消!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.31,0:06:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,修理兩頓!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太吵啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰\N都有想一個人靜一下的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…\N果然艦長是認真囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話,就太過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰勒大人好可憐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以瞭解\N我也有想自己一個人的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.24,0:06:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像是他\N他想自己一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不像他呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.31,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實在這種時候才是\N真正需要我們的時候呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.58,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一次的人生\N不要被人家弄的暈頭轉向的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己喜歡的事情\N依自己的意思去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這事告訴大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.34,0:07:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.41,0:07:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慶泰勒離隊,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中將大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確,失去生氣的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.06,0:07:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有些寂寞吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是這樣\N可是我聽說過一個故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一群猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.41,0:08:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猴子們以首領為頭\N形成有統率的群體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.41,0:08:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是幾年就有一次\N異於這群的猴子一定會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,異端的猴子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.38,0:08:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這隻異端的猴子離開自己的\N族群去接近其他的猴群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.42,0:08:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他族群的猴子不接納異端猴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.43,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙就會\N被修理得滿身是血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.66,0:08:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猴子社會也有像泰勒一樣\N不合群的傢伙嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.33,0:08:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這種不合群的傢伙\N其存在更珍貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其存在才更珍貴…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為猴子們靠異端猴的存在\N才能群體間的血統互相交換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.68,0:08:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防止自己族群血統變的太濃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.78,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,異端猴子對猴群來說\N是不可或缺的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依據自然的哲理\N產出了異端份子出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.29,0:09:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,對我們軍方組織來說\N泰勒也許是這樣的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.79,0:09:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說中將大人的意思\N是軍方需要泰勒這個人囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦,中將大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,異端才是組織的關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.06,0:09:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.86,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就現在來說\N泰勒也許就是這樣的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.01,0:09:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是巡洋艦阿蘇號的艦長嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的\N- 不只是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時已經決定晉升你為上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上…上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘇號的艦長,上尉是配不上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.79,0:10:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘇是我軍技術人員\N集中了所有精美開發出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.09,0:10:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新銳的巡洋艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來是決定交給泰勒來負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個月前發生的事情\N你應該也很清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經過去的事情\N我是不願意再說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.40,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而我認為你才是\N真正適合阿蘇號的艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!非常的光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關船員的遴選\N就遵重你的意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.08,0:10:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你希望的話\N也可以選用微風號原來的船員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,由里子絲達上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.59,0:10:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個月之前就已經被調派為\N情報部作戰司令副官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.23,0:10:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不得選用她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.23,0:10:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡洋艦阿蘇號的下水典禮\N在三天後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對你抱很大的期望\N山本上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.57,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.07,0:10:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我山本作為\N惑星聯合宇宙軍的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.21,0:10:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算粉碎我的身、我的肉\N我的骨頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.24,0:10:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要把這個重要的任務\N好好的完成讓你們看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你趕快去做一切準備吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.81,0:11:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡洋艦阿蘇號艦長山本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.55,0:11:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.10,0:11:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山本新艦長\N好像要召集原微風號的船員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.14,0:11:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不在意嗎?\N上校原來也是微風號的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是微風號的船員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這已經是過去的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去的事了…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.65,0:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微風號的其他船員\N現在都在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.96,0:11:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都遵守泰勒艦長說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照自己的意思\N走自己喜歡的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.92,0:12:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別過來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別過來啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要開始啦,春美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.58,0:13:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.25,0:13:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奉惑星聯合宇宙軍\N山本上校之命來拜訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是山本君送來的,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.09,0:14:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,復歸軍方申請書和…\N到任巡洋艦阿蘇號的派令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.39,0:14:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.43,0:14:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山本君官運也相當不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春美,手術中止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.79,0:15:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中將大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.89,0:15:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新銳的巡洋艦阿蘇號\N下水典禮終於要開始啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.16,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.86,0:15:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們銀河邊境方面\N三船艦隊第1731艘的艦船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於要進行啦,絲達上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.48,0:15:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.08,0:15:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原微風號的各位船員各自依照\N自己選定的路在走不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又回到阿蘇號呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝,上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.36,0:15:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定也是\N大家喜歡而選擇的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.86,0:15:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新出發的人\N和留下來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.03,0:15:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得又高興、又傷心\N真是奇妙的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.77,0:15:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是大家都依照\N自己的心意來集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.21,0:15:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信一定很有幹勁吧\N山本先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.21,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新任艦長\N能搭乘最新銳的新艦出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是非常光榮的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是你所想像的那麼輕鬆喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.85,0:16:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山本先生也經過了\N像山一樣多的辛苦、忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且經過長久的等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.89,0:16:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.90,0:16:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各部門作最終的報告!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內火艇收藏庫,準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.60,0:16:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也沒有問題啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.81,0:16:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥機收藏庫,準備OK!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫務室,各種準備也做好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.45,0:16:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通信機器,一切正常運作!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.85,0:16:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.75,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機關室和航行系統正常!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.92,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廁所、浴室都亮晶晶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股和胸部也亮晶晶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也準備好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好! 好! 好極了!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都準備好…啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋,真好幹勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.87,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,載上高帽的話,連豬都會爬樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.18,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!那麼身為艦長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請下命令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.06,0:18:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼事呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微風號!莫非…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從阿蘇號打來的報告\N用這個全部切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在可能很吵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.98,0:18:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.98,0:18:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一開始的目的\N就是這個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個人一個人\N自己決定的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,依照艦長所說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.06,0:19:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人一個人依照自己的心意\N做了自己喜歡的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走,上校大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 八哥八哥他…\N- 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.02,0:19:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八哥八哥這傢伙…\N比以前做了更奇怪的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙復歸的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.36,0:19:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不能輕視惑星聯合宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心應付才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希哈斯,妳還太單純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.07,0:19:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟在宇宙軍這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能留多久呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.74,0:19:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的才能也許無法計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.45,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.42,0:20:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯巴拉巴．特姆,給你命令!\N再一次把八哥八哥帶到面前來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.92,0:20:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得急著想見到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希哈斯!妳去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始進行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.73,0:20:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收回由里子小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,異端才是…\N組織的關鍵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.72,0:20:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情報作戰司令部\N究竟在做什麼事呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫負責人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.49,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想見見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位不負責任的艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.46,0:20:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主力全開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全速前進!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.53,0:21:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑斯迪．植木．泰勒,二十歲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.43,0:21:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春美君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.54,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.54,0:21:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類這個東西\N還是很不錯的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.43,0:22:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人生路上\N不負責任的人最無憂無慮
